e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"擺係衫入面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"但係日日換衫時拎出黎再放返入去好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"放銀包得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b468dcbe344d3991d17c3fdb48852ecf50a3f1","tid":1842793,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f486ebecf42ad47c4e758ddf6218030599067009","tid":1842793,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2532ffb410ec6251cd442a66e41a6fe1bdee7a33","tid":1842793,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c8765559826b2688292053ade348103fe13d70","tid":1842793,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗錢？麻唔麻煩？如果我沒立定死後孤身一人想知啲人點處理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:26:20.000Z","msg":"幾舊水-千零囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"之後張紙係立係律師？我冇遺囑冇家產立條命同父母合葬得唔得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:28:16.000Z","msg":" 平安紙、遺囑<br />\n遺囑又叫平安紙，是在生前訂立，立囑人去世時便生效，遺囑執行人便按遺囑內容進行財產分配，由於遺囑具備法律上的權威性，有效的遺囑是代表立囑人的合法意願，法律會予以執行，因此，遺囑在很大程度上可以避免後人爭產。簡單內容的遺囑一般收費在1000-1500元。<br />\n<br />\n何時需要辦理遺囑？<br />\n只要年滿18歲，便可以訂立遺囑，不過年輕的時候沒有財產（除非是繼承得來），又未考慮到死亡，簽寫遺囑，就好像變成了老年人才會做的事。因此，基本上有了一定財產項目，又想留下給某些親人，便需要訂立遺囑。<br />\n<br />\n律師辦理遺囑收費？<br />\n遺囑必須乎合法律，，即是香港法例第30章遺囑條例的要求(如見証人、書面方式和簽名)、內容必須清晰，找律師代辦較可靠，因為人死了，遺囑便不能修改。律師辦理簡單的平安紙，一般收費約一千元。<br />\n<br />\n遺囑執行人 (Executor)<br />\n要找「信得過」的人擔任遺囑執行人 (Executor)，避免財產被侵吞，或承辦人辦事不力。遺囑執行人因此往往也是至親，丈夫找太太作執行人便因此很常見。<br />\n<br />\n本律師行《遺囑/平安紙》特色： 快、平。"},{"pid":"f283c1a6453beb450bb20b05f095d47e8e5e075e","tid":1842793,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b57e68b0f426fce136d7758b8877ffabd47900a","tid":1842793,"uid":202593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:27:47.000Z","msg":"會唔會葬嗰陣啲人話唔同輩唔可以合葬㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"唔會呀應該 一家人嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddd8417964c5de870090550aab99c5306866e1f","tid":1842793,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45dc24db324042b54984ee1e885089304223d6f0","tid":1842793,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795cb2599fa271060af9f662badb9d28f354236d","tid":1842793,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"730e53021c7ede4c2ab728cd315b1c7a683da111","tid":1842793,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"擺係衫入面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"但係日日換衫時拎出黎再放返入去好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"放銀包得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"係喎 巴打唔該你<br />\n但應該點寫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}